Things to do for Xfce Panel
===========================

General
-------
 - Fix all the code with TODO in the comment.

Libxfce4panel
-------------
 - Add support for visibility.
 - Plugin visibility support.
 - Test the GObject plugin support.

Panel
-----
 - Stack panels on screen edges.
 - Make struts application wide, we can set one strut for
   each screen.
 - Support for remote plugins.

Plugins
--------
 - Merge the tasklist and the iconbox into one plugin.
 - Possible support for a 'desktop file only' launcher, on plugin
   changes we edit the origional launcher (copy in
   ~/.local/share/applications/).
 - Transparent tray icons.
